# ==========================================================================
# > 拼多多（PDD）防直连、防IP绕过终极分流补丁
# > 专属定制：Hubfilter / QuantumultX
# ==========================================================================

# ----------------- 1. 域名劫持强导（强迫流量过圈X代理层） -----------------
HOST-KEYWORD, pinduoduo, PROXY
HOST-KEYWORD, yangkeduo, PROXY
HOST-SUFFIX, pinduoduo.com, PROXY
HOST-SUFFIX, yangkeduo.com, PROXY

# ----------------- 2. 调度网关阻断（切断阿里系AMDC公共借道） -----------------
HOST, amdc.m.taobao.com, REJECT
HOST, amdc.alipay.com, REJECT

# ----------------- 3. 自治系统号捕获（ASN 级别地毯式拦截） -----------------
# 拦截拼多多官方注册的核心骨干网络 ASN 流量，强制其走代理
IP-ASN, 137452, PROXY, no-resolve
IP-ASN, 139199, PROXY, no-resolve
IP-ASN, 55990, PROXY, no-resolve

# ----------------- 4. 核心 IP CIDR 网段无死角防线 -----------------
# 包含拼多多核心 BGP 机房、CDN 加速节点及内测反代服务器等常见 IP 段
IP-CIDR, 101.33.26.0/23, PROXY, no-resolve
IP-CIDR, 121.5.176.0/21, PROXY, no-resolve
IP-CIDR, 129.226.0.0/16, PROXY, no-resolve
IP-CIDR, 150.109.0.0/16, PROXY, no-resolve
IP-CIDR, 152.136.0.0/16, PROXY, no-resolve
IP-CIDR, 162.14.0.0/16, PROXY, no-resolve
IP-CIDR, 175.24.160.0/19, PROXY, no-resolve
IP-CIDR, 175.27.0.0/19, PROXY, no-resolve
IP-CIDR, 203.205.128.0/17, PROXY, no-resolve
